data-id=\"345805a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3f890d4 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3f890d4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-462bf58 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"462bf58\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Calendar_back-1024x683.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1714\" alt=\"calendar back\" srcset=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Calendar_back-1024x683.png 1024w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Calendar_back-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Calendar_back-768x512.png 768w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Calendar_back.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"  title=\"Modular Magnetic Advent Calendar\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef2b7b3 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ef2b7b3\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a416391 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a416391\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">CAD Render<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-43a3571 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"43a3571\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a25a1ff e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a25a1ff\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e8310bd e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"e8310bd\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-20c2b14 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"20c2b14\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Render_calender_back-1024x683.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1806\" alt=\"render calender back\" srcset=\"https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Render_calender_back-1024x683.png 1024w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Render_calender_back-300x200.png 300w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Render_calender_back-768x512.png 768w, https:\/\/kleophasindel.github.io\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/07\/Render_calender_back.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"  title=\"Modular Magnetic Advent Calendar\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-038478f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"038478f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-48f60af elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"48f60af\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>This project involved the design and manufacture of a modular 25-day advent calendar using Fusion 360 and my personal Bambu Lab A1 Mini 3D printer. The primary design challenge was the printer&#8217;s limited build volume (180 \u00d7 180 \u00d7 180 mm), which would have significantly restricted the size of the drawers if the calendar were printed as a single part.<\/p><p>To overcome this, I designed the calendar as a modular assembly of individual hexagonal cells that can be printed separately and connected using embedded magnets. This approach enabled a larger, more practical design while remaining easy to assemble, disassemble and store.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ae3d83d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ae3d83d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-43a8756 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"43a8756\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Project Information<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ff4a06c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ff4a06c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4c45cca elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"4c45cca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Software<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>Fusion 360<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><strong>Manufacturing<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>FDM 3D Printing<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><strong>Printer<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>Bambu Lab A1 Mini<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><strong>Material<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>PLA<\/p><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><p><strong>Project Type<\/strong><\/p><\/td><td><p>Personal Project<\/p><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e987ed0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e987ed0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d469eec elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d469eec\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Design Highlights<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-568232d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"568232d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9965db1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9965db1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The completed calendar consists of:<\/p><ul><li>25 modular hexagonal cells (5 unique designs depending on their position within the assembly)<\/li><li>25 sliding drawers, each individually numbered<\/li><li>25 interchangeable handles<\/li><li>25 M3 heat-set threaded inserts<\/li><li>25 M3 screws<\/li><li>108 \u00d88 \u00d7 1 mm neodymium magnets<\/li><\/ul><p>Each module was designed as a self-contained unit containing a sliding drawer and magnetic connections to neighbouring cells. The rear face of each module includes either festive artwork or lettering, which together reveal a hidden Christmas message.<\/p><p>To improve durability, the drawer handles are secured using M3 screws threaded into heat-set inserts rather than relying on printed threads. Drawer clearances were designed to provide smooth operation while accounting for typical FDM printing tolerances.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e7b48e1 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e7b48e1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-85477f7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"85477f7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Engineering Considerations<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-947fc9c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"947fc9c\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7f9f5df elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7f9f5df\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>This project provided valuable experience in designing for additive manufacturing and assembly.<\/p><p>During development, several design iterations were made to improve manufacturability. For example, the original decorative snowman design proved too detailed for reliable printing at this scale, so it was simplified to a snowflake design for the final build. Small sacrificial tabs were also added to improve bed adhesion and reduce corner lifting during printing.<\/p><p>These changes allowed the project to be completed successfully while balancing print quality, manufacturing time and available resources.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c3c9fe2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c3c9fe2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Engineering skills aplied<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af50178 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"af50178\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b49c210 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b49c210\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li>Parametric CAD modelling in Fusion 360<\/li><li>Design for Additive Manufacturing (DfAM)<\/li><li>Modular assembly design<\/li><li>Mechanical fastening using heat-set inserts<\/li><li>Magnet integration<\/li><li>Tolerance-aware design<\/li><li>Rapid prototyping and iterative design<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u2190 Back to 3D Printing Projects Modular Magnetic Advent Calendar CAD Render This project involved the design and manufacture of a modular 25-day advent calendar using Fusion 360 and my personal Bambu Lab A1 Mini 3D printer. The primary design challenge was the printer&#8217;s limited build volume (180 \u00d7 180 \u00d7 180 mm), which would [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"no-sidebar","site-content-layout":"page-builder","ast-site-content-layout":"full-width-container","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site-post-title":"disabled","ast-breadcrumbs-content":"","ast-featured-img":"disabled","footer-sml-layout":"","ast-disable-related-posts":"","theme-transparent-header-meta":"","adv-header-id-meta":"","stick-header-meta":"","header-above-stick-meta":"","header-main-stick-meta":"","header-below-stick-meta":"","astra-migrate-meta-layouts":"default","ast-page-background-enabled":"default","ast-page-background-meta":{"desktop":{"background-color":"var(--ast-global-color-4)","background-image":"","background-repeat":"repeat","background-position":"center center","background-size":"auto","background-attachment":"scroll","background-type":"","background-media":"","overlay-type":"","overlay-color":"","overlay-opacity":"","overlay-gradient":""},"tablet":{"background-color":"","background-image":"","background-repeat":"repeat","background-position":"center center","background-size":"auto","background-attachment":"scroll","background-type":"","background-media":"","overlay-type":"","overlay-co